org.apache.ctakes.lvg.ae

Class LvgBaseTokenAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • JCasAnnotator_ImplBase
      • org.apache.ctakes.lvg.ae.LvgBaseTokenAnnotator

  • public class LvgBaseTokenAnnotator
extends JCasAnnotator_ImplBase
    UIMA annotator that uses the UMLS LVG package to find the canonical form of BaseTokens. The package is also used to find one or more lemmas for a given BaseToken along with its associated part of speech.
